</comment>
                            <comment id="13056895" author="rangadi" created="Wed, 29 Jun 2011 00:48:02 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt; if glob or resource matches more than one file, it returns none (must be a typo). This should be a blocker or we should update the release notes?&lt;/p&gt;

